statement.description: shape match { case "rectangle" => scala.StringContext.apply("Area of ", " is ", "").s(shape, f.apply(first, second).toString()) case "square" => if (first.!=(second)) "not defined yet for square" else scala.StringContext.apply("Area of ", " is ", "").s(shape, f.apply(first, second).toString()) case "parallelogram" => scala.StringContext.apply("Area of ", " is ", "").s(shape, f.apply(first, second).toString()) case "rhombus" => scala.StringContext.apply("Area of ", " is ", "").s(shape, f.apply(first, second).toString()) case _ => scala.StringContext.apply("", " is not defined").s(shape) }
